name: Blew
wikiSummary: A testament to how raw Nirvana were at the time: on the first day of the Bleach sessions, Cobain and Novoselic tuned their guitars down two notes, forgetting they had already tuned down from a standard setting.  Blew, a meditation on entrapment and control was even sludgier than they intended.
wikiText:
A testament to how raw Nirvana were at the time: on the first day of the Bleach sessions, Cobain and Novoselic tuned their guitars down two notes, forgetting they had already tuned down from a standard setting.  Blew, a meditation on entrapment and control was even sludgier than they intended.
